    "We are greatly saddened by the untimely passing of our dear Board Chair DeAnne Connolly-Graham which has left a void in many lives and organizations. We are grateful to have had her championing our cause for over 18 years, she has left a magnificent legacy.",
    "To honor and remember her, AYUDA has created the DeAnne Connolly Graham Legacy Fund We hope to see you on October 28 for her &#8220;Celebration of Life.&#8221; Please see below:",
